:INFO
FAQs for a Trades Portfolio Website
Common questions to answer on your trades website FAQ page. Answering these builds trust and helps with local SEO.

:TASK
[ ] Do you offer emergency or after-hours service?
[ ] What areas do you serve?
[ ] Are you licensed and insured?
[ ] Do you provide free estimates?
[ ] How do I prepare for a technician visit?
[ ] What payment methods do you accept?
[ ] How long does a typical job take?
[ ] Do you warranty your work?

:NOTE
Write the FAQ answers in plain language, one to three sentences each. Avoid jargon. These pages often rank for question-based local searches and can drive qualified leads without paid ads.

